<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1 Vangkhuo minthang Bethlehem ah,
 Singkhuol singzatam lai ah;
 Lal Krista mimbang a hung pieng,
 Bethlehem bawng In tawm ah,

[V2]
 Lampak hitiu (2)
 Zatam ding a hung pieng chu (2)

[V3]
 2. Sietlei hingmi zatam lai ah,
 Amah bang him pieng puonna;
 Angel leh Serafimte chun,
 Zaila lopi'n a hun thau

[V4]
 Chungnung pen ah (2)
 Hossana Lal lopi chu (2)

[V5]
 3. Michingte leh Be!ampute,
 Gam vangla a pat hung ui;
 A chunnu Mari anglai ah;
 Va muu ui sambang zalin.

[V6]
 Kipak tak leh lawptak mai in.
 Lal thak chibai a buk ui (2)

[V7]
 4. Angel lopi hung tuolkum in,
 Bethlehem zaila'n awi ui;
 Chamna Lal mimbang hung pieng chu,
 Zaila hawih lopi'n thau ui.

[V8]
 Halleluijah (2)
 Lalthak mimbang hung pieng chu. (2)

[V9]
 5. Mimbang pienna nuoi simlei ah,
 Lieng chungchuong ie Hukdampa;
 Ka suihlung bawng In tawm sung ah,
 Hungpieng kitin vawnsen in.

[V10]
 Chun thehnem in (2)
 Hui ingka ka kumsawt Lal.</lyrics>
<title>Bethlehem Ah</title>
<hymn_number>30</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Thanglal</author>
</song>